data.description: Hidden Gem with great potential 3/1 in main house 1/1 with separate entrance in rear (attached). Excellent opportunity for extended family or rental income. Shingle Roof Replaced 2012, flat roof 2023, a/c 2011. Kitchen and appliances updated 2016. Over 7 different fruit trees/plants. Exterior painted 2023, Hurricane shutters. City recently re-did sewer connection and water supply to all homes in the neighborhood and will be repaving streets. Excellent access to Florida Turnpike just 1 minute away.
